# 🚀 Day 07 – Continuous Deployment (CD)

## 📖 Overview

Day 7 marks the completion of the ShopSphere Production-Ready DevOps Challenge.

The objective was to automate the deployment process so that every successful code change pushed to GitHub is automatically built, stored, and deployed to the production server with minimal manual intervention.

This completes the Continuous Deployment (CD) stage of the CI/CD pipeline.

