# 🔄 Rollback Strategy

If deployment fails,

Pull the previous Docker image.

Example

```bash
docker pull backend-2

docker pull frontend-2
```

Update

```
docker-compose.prod.yml
```

Restart

```bash
docker compose down

docker compose up -d
```

Application is restored to the previous stable version.

